      "content": "1. Emphasize the importance of a clean-shaven face, as it conveys authority and professionalism.\n2. Suggest that employees avoid wearing flashy or overly casual clothing, as it can undermine their perceived competence.\n3. Advise against wearing any form of jewelry, as it can be distracting and detract from the seriousness of the meeting.\n4. Recommend that employees maintain a neat and tidy appearance, as it reflects their attention to detail and respect for the meeting.\n5. Encourage the use of a strong, confident posture and a firm handshake, as these non-verbal cues can enhance their authority and presence in the room.",
